metadata.name: Facetastic #1
metadata.description: Facetastic is a one-of-a-kind NFT project that brings together the weirdest and wackiest faces you've ever seen! From twisted noses to bizarrely shaped ears, Facetastic has it all. With an exclusive collection of NFTs featuring these eclectic and eccentric faces, you can be the proud owner of a digital masterpiece that will make your friends do a double take. So why wait? Join the Facetastic craze and add some quirkiness to your NFT collection today!
